Here are the updated patch notes for aim_openfire_v1.2:

-Added light!

-Expanded the map and added new crates and two bunkers on either side

-No more buy menu! Terrorists and Counter-terrorists get their own primary guns to start the round

-Retextured some props

-Overall map height was lowered to make it feel more realistic

========================================================

Hotfixes:

-Increased the height of the map to avoid collision
